data.description: Custom-built stunning home on 1/2 acre offers a perfect balance of rustic charm, modern convenience & industrial touches for unique flair. Quality shines w/ impressive steel railings, wood lined cathedral ceiling, polished concrete countertops, stunning solid wood doors & cabinets & designer lighting throughout. Luxury radiates in the primary ensuite bath w/ free-standing soaking tub, custom shelving & huge shower leading to a dreamy walk-in closet. The finished basement offers a theater space or private getaway & potential wine cellar! A separate detached studio w/ 1/2 bath, w/d hookups & outdoor shower add entertainment/living space. Shop/Studio opportunity w/ foundation poured & utilities in, permit expired but plans provided. No HOA!
